以下是一些使用 `serde_json::to_string` 的範例，這些範例展示了不同的資料結構和資料類型序列化的情況：

### 範例 1：序列化結構體

```rust
use serde::{Serialize, Deserialize};

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
struct User {
    name: String,
    age: u32,
}

fn main() {
    let user = User {
        name: String::from("Alice"),
        age: 30,
    };
    let serialized = serde_json::to_string(&user).unwrap();
    println!("{}", serialized);
}
```

### 範例 2：序列化列舉

```rust
use serde::{Serialize, Deserialize};

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
enum Message {
    Quit,
    ChangeColor(u32, u32, u32),
}

fn main() {
    let msg = Message::ChangeColor(255, 0, 0);
    let serialized = serde_json::to_string(&msg).unwrap();
    println!("{}", serialized);
}
```

### 範例 3：序列化列表（向量）

```rust
use serde::{Serialize, Deserialize};

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
struct Inventory {
    items: Vec<String>,
}

fn main() {
    let inventory = Inventory {
        items: vec![String::from("Sword"), String::from("Shield"), String::from("Potion")],
    };
    let serialized = serde_json::to_string(&inventory).unwrap();
    println!("{}", serialized);
}
```

### 範例 4：序列化字典（雜湊映射）

```rust
use serde::{Serialize, Deserialize};
use std::collections::HashMap;

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
struct Config {
    settings: HashMap<String, String>,
}

fn main() {
    let mut settings = HashMap::new();
    settings.insert(String::from("volume"), String::from("75"));
    settings.insert(String::from("brightness"), String::from("60"));

    let config = Config { settings };
    let serialized = serde_json::to_string(&config).unwrap();
    println!("{}", serialized);
}
```

### 範例 5：序列化嵌套結構

```rust
use serde::{Serialize, Deserialize};

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
struct Address {
    city: String,
    country: String,
}

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
struct Person {
    name: String,
    age: u32,
    address: Address,
}

fn main() {
    let person = Person {
        name: String::from("Bob"),
        age: 28,
        address: Address {
            city: String::from("New York"),
            country: String::from("USA"),
        },
    };
    let serialized = serde_json::to_string(&person).unwrap();
    println!("{}", serialized);
}
```

### 範例 6：序列化可選類型（Option）

```rust
use serde::{Serialize, Deserialize};

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
struct Product {
    id: u32,
    name: String,
    description: Option<String>, // 可選的描述欄位
}

fn main() {
    let product = Product {
        id: 1,
        name: String::from("Gadget"),
        description: None, // 此產品沒有描述
    };
    let serialized = serde_json::to_string(&product).unwrap();
    println!("{}", serialized);
}
```

